{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"銀ねこアトリエ"}},"allFile":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"entry442","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#48a8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/88c96/entry442.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/15952/entry442.jpg 375w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/cd750/entry442.jpg 750w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/5caa2/entry442.jpg 1080w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/88c96/entry442.jpg 1200w","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/fd9fd/entry442.webp 375w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/e56aa/entry442.webp 750w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/257a3/entry442.webp 1080w,\n/static/ac9b62eed8697643d207b9a75f009e33/296b8/entry442.webp 1200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"}]},"width":1200,"height":900}}}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b95d7e97-6aa4-5719-91d0-28046d0f1b70","excerpt":"Aceエディターとは？ 出会いは必然にして突然。。。 今回お仕事で出会った、JS製埋め込み式エディターの使い方をご紹介します。  Ace is an embeddable code editor written in JavaScript.\nAceはJSで書かれた埋め込み可能なエディター。 https://ace.c…","html":"<h2 id=\"aceエディターとは？\">Aceエディターとは？</h2>\n<p>出会いは必然にして突然。。。</p>\n<p>今回お仕事で出会った、JS製埋め込み式エディターの使い方をご紹介します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/4b190/entry442-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.0126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/81b7c/entry442-0.webp 158w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/6ea66/entry442-0.webp 315w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/8aab1/entry442-0.webp 630w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/d00b9/entry442-0.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/ff44c/entry442-0.jpg 158w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/a6688/entry442-0.jpg 315w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/828fb/entry442-0.jpg 630w,\n/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/4b190/entry442-0.jpg 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/91da174c9b7d2655d51db2112ecbc6f4/828fb/entry442-0.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Aceエディター JS\"\n            title=\"Aceエディター JS\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ace is an embeddable code editor written in JavaScript.<br>\nAceはJSで書かれた埋め込み可能なエディター。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://ace.c9.io/\">https://ace.c9.io/</a></p>\n<p>コードを紹介するためのエディターというよりはむしろ、コードを書くためのエディターを埋め込めるライブラリです。</p>\n<h3 id=\"特徴\">特徴</h3>\n<p>めっちゃ高機能です。主には以下のような特徴があります。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>110以上の言語をサポート</li>\n<li>20以上のテーマ</li>\n<li>膨大な行でも大丈夫（100万行以下）</li>\n<li>正規表現で置換や検索が使える</li>\n<li>リアルタイムでチェック可能 (現在JavaScript/CoffeeScript/CSS/XQuery)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"aceエディター基本の使い方\">Aceエディター基本の使い方</h2>\n<p>では、実際に実装してみましょう！\nリファレンスを参考にしつつ、CDNに上がっているライブラリを使ってみます。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ace/1.2.0/ace.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>以下のような設定にします。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>言語・JS</li>\n<li>ID「editor」のタグにセット</li>\n<li>テーマ「monokai」とつかう</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">min-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ace/1.2.0/ace.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> editor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ace<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">edit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    theme<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ace/theme/monokai\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    mode<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ace/mode/javascript\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    minLines<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>コードはシンプルに7行。</p>\n<p>カンタンに実装できました！！</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/4b190/entry442-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.51898734177215%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/81b7c/entry442-1.webp 158w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/6ea66/entry442-1.webp 315w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/8aab1/entry442-1.webp 630w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/d00b9/entry442-1.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/ff44c/entry442-1.jpg 158w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/a6688/entry442-1.jpg 315w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/828fb/entry442-1.jpg 630w,\n/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/4b190/entry442-1.jpg 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/df2de823709ba2e3936ce0228b7a4bbf/828fb/entry442-1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Aceエディター\"\n            title=\"Aceエディター\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>実際にテキスト（JS）を打ち込んでみるときちんとハイライトがリアルタイムで効きます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/84f0d/entry442-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.759493670886075%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/81b7c/entry442-2.webp 158w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/6ea66/entry442-2.webp 315w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/8aab1/entry442-2.webp 630w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/59680/entry442-2.webp 632w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/ff44c/entry442-2.jpg 158w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/a6688/entry442-2.jpg 315w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/828fb/entry442-2.jpg 630w,\n/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/84f0d/entry442-2.jpg 632w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7dcd78d8d01f1a05a2b794abb83ef7da/828fb/entry442-2.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Aceエディター JS\"\n            title=\"Aceエディター JS\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>エディター上でCmd+Fを押すと検索バーが出てくるというスグレモノ。。。すげー高機能です。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/67e9d/entry442-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.78481012658228%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/81b7c/entry442-3.webp 158w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/6ea66/entry442-3.webp 315w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/8aab1/entry442-3.webp 630w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/457aa/entry442-3.webp 710w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/ff44c/entry442-3.jpg 158w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/a6688/entry442-3.jpg 315w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/828fb/entry442-3.jpg 630w,\n/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/67e9d/entry442-3.jpg 710w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/52b33a39bcb48d830e935b4f93903a0d/828fb/entry442-3.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Aceエディター 検索バー\"\n            title=\"Aceエディター 検索バー\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"いくつかの実装方法をご紹介\">いくつかの実装方法をご紹介</h3>\n<p>ID「editor」にセットした場合の説明です。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">min-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ace/1.2.0/ace.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> editor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ace<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">edit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 続きを書く</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>要素にエディターをセットしてテーマや言語などをあとで設定も可能です。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// テーマ追加</span>\neditor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ace/theme/monokai\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 言語設定</span>\neditor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setMode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ace/mode/javascript\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>テーマを確認したいときはこちらをご覧ください。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ace.c9.io/build/kitchen-sink.html\">https://ace.c9.io/build/kitchen-sink.html</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"オプションだけ渡すパターン\">オプションだけ渡すパターン</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setOptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  autoScrollEditorIntoView<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  copyWithEmptySelection<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"オプションを取得\">オプションを取得</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getOption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"optionName\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"折り返しをつける\">折り返しをつける</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setUseWrapMode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"タブサイズ変更\">タブサイズ変更</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setTabSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"文字の挿入\">文字の挿入</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'文字'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"カーソルの位置を取得\">カーソルの位置を取得</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>selection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getCursor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"ソフトタブの使用（タブにスペースを使用）\">ソフトタブの使用（タブにスペースを使用）</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setUseSoftTabs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"フォントサイズ設定\">フォントサイズ設定</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setFontSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">14</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"ボタンを利用してコード内のテキストに文字を追加したい\">ボタンを利用してコード内のテキストに文字を追加したい</h2>\n<p>コード内にボタンを使ってタグやテキストをを追加したい場合です。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>insert-btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文字を挿入<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">editor.selection.getCursor()</code>でエディター内のカーソルのある位置を取得して、<code class=\"language-text\"> editor.session.insert()</code>で文字列を挿入します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#insert-btn\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>selection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getCursor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;strong>よくできました！！&lt;/strong>\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/4b190/entry442-4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.68354430379747%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/81b7c/entry442-4.webp 158w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/6ea66/entry442-4.webp 315w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/8aab1/entry442-4.webp 630w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/d00b9/entry442-4.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/ff44c/entry442-4.jpg 158w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/a6688/entry442-4.jpg 315w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/828fb/entry442-4.jpg 630w,\n/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/4b190/entry442-4.jpg 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5a806075ae58a5d85cc7ab8e3842ef8c/828fb/entry442-4.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Aceエディター\"\n            title=\"Aceエディター\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"コードの内容を他のフォームに移動\">コードの内容を他のフォームに移動</h2>\n<p>今回やったのが任意のフォームパーツ（テキストエリア）へAceエディターに入力された内容を転記するというものでした。</p>\n<p>textareaにhtmlコードを記載したかったので、どうしてもAceエディターが使いたかったです。</p>\n<p><br>Aceエディターに変更があったらテキストエリアの内容も変更できるようにしました。</p>\n<h3 id=\"htmlの紹介\">HTMLの紹介</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">min-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>texstarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>none</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>texarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"jsコードの紹介\">JSコードの紹介</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> textarea <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'textarea[name=\"message\"]'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\neditor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>textarea<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">val</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Aceエディター内の変更があれば中身をtextareaのvalueとしてセット</span>\neditor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'change'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  textarea<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">val</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>これでコードを書き換えるたび、コードが任意の<code class=\"language-text\">textarea</code>タグに転記されていい感じになりました！</p>\n<h2 id=\"トグルボタンでテキストエリアのサイズ変更\">トグルボタンでテキストエリアのサイズ変更</h2>\n<p>次にやりたかったのが、コードを各エリアのサイズ変更です。</p>\n<p>AceエディターはJSを読み込んだ時に、サイズを取得します。なのでエリアのサイズ変更する場合は再読み込みしなければなりません。</p>\n<p>なので<code class=\"language-text\">const editor = ace.edit(\"editor\");</code>などで作成したAceエディターを一度削除する必要があります。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>resize-btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>入力欄を拡大する<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>JSコードです。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">destroy()</code>で作ったAceエディターの設定を削除し、htmlのコードも削除します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// エディターをタグにセット</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> editor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ace<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">edit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 初期化用の関数</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">aceinit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">editor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setFontSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">14</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setMode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ace/mode/html\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setUseWrapMode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setTabSize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//初期化</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">aceinit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#resize-btn\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// #editorの設定したを削除</span>\n    editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">destroy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//htmlも削除</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//高さでサイズ変更</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#editor\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"600\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"toke